==Untitled==
alexandru averescu was born in babele which is close to izmail, but not in the city itself, hence the renaming of the village to averescu.

==Ozyornoye==
Actually, in 1859, when he was born, his hometown (and the whole Southern Bessarabia) was part of the "United Principalities of Wallachia and Moldavia", so its name was "Babele". :-) [[User:Bogdangiusca|bogdan]] 15:10, 28 October 2006 (UTC)
